Multiple Jobs in Alcon Aluminium
|
Thursday, 1 May 2014
10:30 am
Jobs in Pakistan
A leading Aluminium manufacturing & service provider company in Lahore is looking for:
1) Area Manager (Sales & Marketing)
ÿ For Lahore, Faisalabad, Multan & Sialkot
ÿ BSc, BBA, MBA from Recognized university
ÿ 5-7 years of experience in sales. Preferably in building material products.
2) Area Executive (Sales & Marketing)
ÿ Lahore Based position
ÿ FA. FSC, Civil Diploma or equal.
ÿ 2-3 years of experience in sales & marketing. Preferably in building material
products.
3) Structure Engineer
ÿ Min 5 years industry experience in structural engineering with specialization in
Facad. Preferably in building material products.
We offer attractive salary package, opportunities for professional growth & career
development, in line with the significant contribution expected from this position.
Procedure to Apply:
Please email your CV with latest photograph at: HRALCON.CV@GMAIL.COM
Please Mention the” Position applied for” in the subject line.
